{"tid":421614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（上帝的憤怒）教宗反加獨：民族主義毀歐盟夢想","createTime":"2017-10-02T11:28:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-04T15:28:47.000Z","uid":41351,"like":4,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"efcc5efc5c0e6295a95fc42d4c5d8d3cc39f8269","tid":421614,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕加泰隆尼亞舉行獨立公投，西班牙政府以違憲為由，派遣警察阻止投票，也因此與民眾發生衝突，但這絲毫不影響加泰隆尼亞當地的決心，有90%選民投下贊成票。不過，天主教教宗方濟各（Pope Francis）昨（1）日卻說，最近歐洲的民粹主義和民族主義運動正在威脅到和平。<br />\n綜合外媒報導，方濟各於昨日造訪義大利的波隆那，在對現場的大學生的演講時，雖然未直接提到加泰隆尼亞的獨立公投，以及警察的暴力鎮壓行為，但方濟各卻指出：歐洲是在戰爭的餘燼中重生並獲得和平，而「衝突以及其它利益正威脅這些創建時的理想」，並呼籲「不要懼怕團結」，「希望特殊利益以及國家主義，不會讓歐盟創立者振奮人心的夢想白費。」<br />\n另外，教廷梵蒂岡曾公開表示，不支持加泰隆尼亞自治政府獨立。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2210770\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2210770&d=C9qNgtEUKlqkss9eVJ5ZFv755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=ff0caa4e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2210770&h=7c024aa6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2210770</a><br />\n教宗怒了<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/02/192810_3c2f8d9adeaf578058e08ea6a8e3f06c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F02%2F192810_3c2f8d9adeaf578058e08ea6a8e3f06c.jpg&h=51b698b4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5cb6548e90548bb7818e3b216c4e6e7c0377bab1","tid":421614,"uid":40216,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:30:58.000Z","msg":"左膠越反對，我就越支持"},{"pid":"027ac7d299bb15223563af91fe0b849741cb714f","tid":421614,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-02T11:31:31.000Z","msg":"教宗都唔幫人權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faa2345a3bbae2bf7a4bf04d90dacfcde3bb8458","tid":421614,"uid":35870,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"